nodes.text: Obi-Wan Kenobi's taskforce was a task force commanded during the Clone Wars by Jedi General Obi-Wan Kenobi.

Obi-Wan Kenobi's taskforce consisted of at least three Venator-class Star Destroyers, including the flagship Negotiator. During an attack against the fleet, it also consisted at least three Arquitens-class light cruisers and at least two Consular-class cruisers.
